expression: text
---
Full-text search across sessions

Usage: cdt search [OPTIONS] <QUERY>

Arguments:
  <QUERY>  Search query

Options:
      --format <FORMAT>    Output format [default: table] [possible values: json, jsonl, table]
      --limit <LIMIT>      Max results [default: 50]
      --offset <OFFSET>    Offset for pagination [default: 0]
      --project <PROJECT>  Scope to a project (name or encoded ID; use --project=<id> for encoded IDs)
      --json[=<JSON>]      Select JSON fields (comma-separated), implies --format json. Without value: list available fields. Usage: --json=field1,field2
      --session <SESSION>  Scope to a single session (intra-session search)
      --no-truncate        Do not truncate fields in table mode
      --since <SINCE>      Only search sessions after this time
  -v, --verbose...         Increase diagnostic verbosity (-v warn, -vv info, -vvv debug). All output is silent by default; `RUST_LOG` overrides this entirely
      --root <ROOT>        Override the data root for this invocation (supports ~/). Temporary, not persisted; takes precedence over the configured claudeRootPath [aliases: --data-dir]
  -h, --help               Print help
